New information decoded from thousands of emails between the Guptas and their associates reveal how South Africa's parastatals and politicians have been captured. A series of stories by amaBhungane and Scorpio, the Daily Maverick's new investigative unit, give explosive details into deals between the Guptas and Chinese-owned companies vying for South African contracts, how politicians and State officials assist the Guptas in these deals and the benefits they receive in return. We spoke to amaBhungane's Craig McKune, who outlined what was in the Gupta's emails and what they mean for State Capture. Here are the five things you need to know about the Gupta Leaks: